General.Name: Intelicare Holdings Ltd
General.Description: Intelicare Holdings Limited engages in the sale of a predictive analytics hardware and software package for use in the aged care and health industries in Australia. The company offers InteliLiving for seniors and people with disability; and produces monitoring solution for seniors and at-risk individuals. Intelicare Holdings Limited was founded in 2016 and is headquartered in Leederville, Australia.
